{
  "stem": "24242.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a town.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little town.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] you had to feed people, right?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they had a place where to keep the groceries, food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A man was in charge of that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was cooks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were people to fix the shoe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were people to fix a rifle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were people that they could entertain you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, they had entertainment, and how.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of entertainment?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Singing, obvious, Russian style.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They had very beautiful-- and there were dancers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was beautiful singers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They would make a stage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They would make a stage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like a little town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You get up in the morning, you wash your face, and each one had a responsibility.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This one stands guard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This one washes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The other one fixes the shoe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The other one-- the third one fixes a rifle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a little town built.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the word got around to the Russian partisans that you go to the Bielskis, and you get anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You want to fix-- you want to fix a rifle?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They'll fix it for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You want to fix a coat or a jacket, they'll fix it for you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, they wouldn't get paid for their service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exchange of favors, I would assume so.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you exactly exchange.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Look, I was a kid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you'll feed me, I'll apparently do something for you if you will ask me to, if I can.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A human exchange, but no money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had problems with the Russian partisans too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- some of them were anti-Semites, Jew haters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
